articles.author: Benjamin Parkin, Jyotsna Singh, Chris Kay, John Reed
articles.title: Narendra Modi set to lose parliamentary majority in shock Indian election result - Financial Times
articles.description: Stock market tumbles as vote counts point to ruling BJP relying on allies to secure historic third term in power
articles.content:
Narendra Modis Bharatiya Janata party is set to lose its parliamentary majority, forcing the Indian prime minister to rely on smaller allies to secure a historic third term.
